SEASON ground beef with salt, if desired, and brown in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat; drain if desired. ADD 1 3/4 cup water and Knorr(R) Fiesta Sides(TM) - Mexican Rice and cook covered according to package directions. ARRANGE rice mixture on serving platter, then top with lettuce, cheese and tomato. Serve, if desired, topped with your favorite taco toppings such as guacamole, sliced olives, sliced pickled jalapeno peppers and/or sour cream.